name: ax-platform
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ax-platform" %}
{% set version = "0.2.5.1" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/ax-platform-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 58f38a90df24427a10872858fbcbc987df3e1560f354020a9d8fa26cc0242802

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.7
    - setuptools >=34.4
    - setuptools-scm
  run:
    - botorch ==0.6.4
    - jinja2
    - multipledispatch
    - sqlalchemy
    - pandas
    - plotly
    - python >=3.7
    - scikit-learn
    - scipy
    - typeguard

test:
  imports:
    - ax
    - ax.benchmark
    - ax.benchmark.methods
    - ax.benchmark.problems

    - ax.benchmark.problems.baseline_results.synthetic

    - ax.benchmark.problems.hpo
    - ax.benchmark.tests
    - ax.core

    - ax.early_stopping.tests
    - ax.exceptions

    - ax.global_stopping.tests
    - ax.metrics
    - ax.metrics.tests
    - ax.modelbridge
    - ax.modelbridge.strategies
    - ax.modelbridge.tests
    - ax.modelbridge.transforms
    - ax.models
    - ax.models.discrete
    - ax.models.numpy
    - ax.models.random
    - ax.models.tests
    - ax.models.torch
    - ax.models.torch.botorch_modular
    - ax.models.torch.tests
    - ax.plot

    - ax.plot.js

    - ax.plot.tests
